# Sprint 57: PWA React — Header, Tracking Player, Loader, Modals (Implementation)
# S57.ptl

v:4
role: planner
gate: OPEN

objective: |
  Implement unified Header (expand/collapse system bar, screen-specific left content),
  Tracking Player (split map + action, timeline, controls), Logo/Loader (full-fill
  and notification), modal unification, and animations. Verify API calls (Object Details
  history, tracking execute, report build), map render for objects/history, and report
  results (scrollable table with fixed first column). Preserve visual perception;
  follow S56 roadmap and state architecture.

requires: [FRONTEND_DEV]
invariants: sprints/54/INVARIANTS.md
design-ref: sprints/56/artifacts/S56-Consolidated-Roadmap.md, sprints/56/artifacts/S56-State-Architecture-Proposal.md, sprints/56/artifacts/S56-Navigation-Flow.md, sprints/56/artifacts/S56-Loading-Lifecycle.md

